From 77cdc29f857847dd1dea51eb20ae539cd9a3f904 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 1 Aug 2025 00:41:57 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:CP:hostapd: ATF: add support for atf group commands

Introduced CLI commands to manage Airtime Fairness (ATF)
using SSID group configurations.
The following commands are added:

atfssidgroup       : Enable group-based ATF configuration
g_atfssidgroup     : Query whether ATF group configuration is enabled
addatfgroup        : Add a new ATF group
configatfgroup     : Configure parameters for an existing ATF group
delatfgroup        : Delete a previously added ATF group
showatfgroup       : Display all configured ATF groups
MLO:
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> [-l <link_id>] atf_offload  atfssidgroup <0/1>
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> [-l <link_id>] atf_offload  g_atfssidgroup
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> [-l <link_id>] atf_offload addatfgroup
<group ame> <ssid name>
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> [-l <link_id>] atf_offload configatfgroup
<group name> <airtime %>
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> [-l <link_id>] atf_offload delatfgroup <groupname>
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> [-l <link_id>] atf_offload showatfgroup 

Legacy:
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> atf_offload  atfssidgroup <0/1>
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> atf_offload  g_atfssidgroup
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> atf_offload addatfgroup <group ame> <ssid name>
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> atf_offload configatfgroup <group name> <airtime %>
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> atf_offload  delatfgroup <groupname>
hostapd_cli -i <ifname> atf_offload  showatfgroup 

Signed-off-by: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
